                        Server side - nodeJs
    
    1. npm init (Installs package.json)

    2. Create index.js

    3. Install express (npm i express)

    4. Import express to index.js

    5. Create an app using express
    

                    Middleware
    1. Application specific Middleware
        Available in entire app.

    2. Router specific Middleware
        Available in specific routers only.

                    JWT token for authentication
    
    npm i jsonwebtoken

    Token generation
    Token verification

    Mongoose helps to connect the server to DB
    

    Front-end backend integration

    Cors(Cross origin resource sharing)
        npm i Cors
        